{% layout 'theme' %}

<style>
  .hh-page { background:#080808; color:#f2ede1; font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; min-height:60vh; }
  .hh-page-inner { max-width:780px; margin:0 auto; padding:80px 48px; }
  .hh-page h1 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:42px; font-weight:400; color:#f2ede1; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .hh-page-rule { width:48px; height:1px; background:#C4A843; margin-bottom:48px; }
  .hh-faq-item { border-bottom:1px solid #1f1a14; padding:24px 0; }
  .hh-faq-q { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.04em; color:#f2ede1; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .hh-faq-a { font-size:13px; color:rgba(242,237,225,0.55); line-height:1.9; font-weight:300; }
  @media(max-width:768px){ .hh-page-inner{ padding:56px 24px; } .hh-page h1{ font-size:32px; } }
</style>

<div class="hh-page">
  <div class="hh-page-inner">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <div class="hh-page-rule"></div>

    <div class="hh-faq-item">
      <p class="hh-faq-q">What materials are your pieces made from?</p>
      <p class="hh-faq-a">All Humble Hearted jewelry is crafted from 18k gold vermeil over sterling silver. Our pieces are nickel-free, hypoallergenic, and built to last with proper care.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hh-faq-item">
      <p class="hh-faq-q">How long does shipping take?</p>
      <p class="hh-faq-a">Standard shipping within the US takes 5&ndash;7 business days. Expedited options are available at checkout. Orders over $75 qualify for free standard shipping.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hh-faq-item">
      <p class="hh-faq-q">Do you ship internationally?</p>
      <p class="hh-faq-a">Yes, we ship to most countries worldwide. International shipping times vary by destination and typically range from 10&ndash;21 business days. Duties and taxes may apply.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hh-faq-item">
      <p class="hh-faq-q">What is your return policy?</p>
      <p class="hh-faq-a">We accept returns within 60 days of purchase on unworn items in original condition. Please visit our Returns page for full details and to initiate a return.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hh-faq-item">
      <p class="hh-faq-q">How do I care for my jewelry?</p>
      <p class="hh-faq-a">To preserve the finish, avoid exposure to water, perfume, lotions, and harsh chemicals. Store pieces in a cool, dry place. See our Materials &amp; Care page for detailed guidance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hh-faq-item">
      <p class="hh-faq-q">Do you offer gift wrapping?</p>
      <p class="hh-faq-a">Every Humble Hearted order arrives in our signature packaging, ready to gift. A complimentary gift message card can be added at checkout.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hh-faq-item">
      <p class="hh-faq-q">How do I find my ring or bracelet size?</p>
      <p class="hh-faq-a">Visit our Size Guide page for printable sizing tools and measuring instructions to find your perfect fit.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hh-faq-item">
      <p class="hh-faq-q">Can I make changes to my order after placing it?</p>
      <p class="hh-faq-a">Order changes can be requested within 2 hours of purchase. Please contact us immediately via our Contact page and we will do our best to accommodate your request before the order ships.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
